# Rakesh Roushan - Personal Site

## Project Overview
Personal portfolio + marketing site at roushanrakesh.com. Monorepo with strategy docs.

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Astro 6 (App Router pattern, Content Collections, MDX)
- **Language**: TypeScript (strict mode)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS 4 with CSS variables (oklch color space)
- **Interactive**: React islands for Three.js, AI chat, and forms
- **CMS**: Keystatic (git-based, TypeScript schemas)
- **Hosting**: Cloudflare Workers via @astrojs/cloudflare adapter
- **Package Manager**: pnpm workspaces + Turborepo

## Key Conventions
- Dark-first design with oklch color tokens
- Astro components for static content, React islands only where interactivity is needed (`client:visible`, `client:load`)
- Content in `src/content/` managed by Astro Content Collections
- Data files (experience, socials) in `src/data/`
- Section components in `src/components/sections/`
- Minimal JS shipped to client — zero JS by default

## Directory Structure
```
apps/web/src/
  components/sections/  — Page sections (Hero, About, Experience, etc.)
  components/3d/        — Three.js React islands
  components/ui/        — Shared UI components
  content/posts/        — MDX blog posts
  data/                 — TypeScript data files
  layouts/              — Astro layouts
  pages/                — Astro pages (file-based routing)
  styles/               — Global CSS
  lib/                  — Utilities
docs/                   — Strategy & company docs (markdown)
```

## Code Style
- Use Astro components (.astro) for static sections
- Use React (.tsx) only for interactive islands
- Tailwind utility classes, no CSS modules
- Keep components focused and composable
- No Framer Motion — use CSS animations or Astro view transitions
